{"tid":758663,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人仲記得海闊天空 地久天長 依兩本書？","createTime":"2018-07-28T02:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T07:31:37.000Z","uid":22349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb4ca24e329e9458da3c8e221f4cc6decf92eceb","tid":758663,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:37:10.000Z","msg":"海闊天空 - 一位血友病者的生命扎記 <br />\n<br />\n　　在面對生命與疾病的道路上，有人選擇自怨自艾地放棄，有人選擇勇敢積極地向前。一對在患難中經歷了無數考驗的母子─ 子鶩及其母親李慧珍女士，用生命和熱誠分別寫下了《海闊天空》及《地久天長》兩本令人動容的著作。這兩本書不但記錄了子鶩及李慧珍女士的心路歷程，同時也展示了他們堅毅不屈的精神和鬥志。 <br />\n　　 <br />\n　　子鶩從小患有先天性血友病，後來因為輸血而無辜地感染了愛滋病。他在世的日子只有短短的二十三年，但他卻用有限的生命去散發出無限的光采，並在離開前完成了《海闊天空》。子鶩在書中敘述了他與一群病友的生命故事，以及他與身邊的人如何互相鼓勵和扶持，並肩走過每個生與死的邊緣。他努力生存的決心，激勵了他身邊的每一個人，讓他們領悟到生命的真正意義和價值。 <br />\n　　 <br />\n　　在子鶩離世後，他的母親李慧珍女士為延續兒子的心願，於是執筆寫作，並且幫助其他愛滋病患者在僅存的日子裏活得有意義和有尊嚴。而在《地久天長》一書中，她記述了自己在兒子患病期間的經歷與感受。她看著兒子遭受疾病的折磨，雖然痛心，但仍無怨無悔地盡力幫助他活出堅強和豐盛的生命。她對兒子的愛以及母愛的偉大，在書中完完全全地表露無遺。 <br />\n　　 <br />\n　　在《海闊天空》及《地久天長》兩本書中，沒有煽情造作的文句，只有真摯坦率的情感與體會。當中的每字每句都有血有淚，觸動著每一位讀者的心靈深處。這兩本著作後來更被改編成為舞台劇及電影；而《海闊天空》亦曾獲得了多個文藝獎以及好書獎。 <br />\n　　子鶩與李慧珍女士的勇氣以及對生命的執著與堅持，不但值得我們的尊敬和學習，更鼓勵了我們在面對困難和逆境時，不應該輕言放棄。子鶩說：「生命是一支燃燒著的蠟燭，沒有人知道燭光會在哪一刻熄滅，但這並不重要；重要的是我們能否用盡這支蠟燭的每分每吋，為生命帶來光，帶來熱」。生命縱然有限，然而只要能夠活得精彩和有意義，便已不枉此生了。 <br />\n　　 　 <br />\n　　 <br />\n　　註：子鶩的「鶩」是野鴨的其中一種，不能高飛。子鶩認為自己是一隻醜小鴨，盼望有一天能夠變成天鵝，完成心願。而他的心願就是寫作，讓更多的人認識愛滋病。"},{"pid":"4b20279ceadb92636a0322e6b2d3fd8d19c753b2","tid":758663,"uid":30272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/104154_d024b75529cbd1063709822da74dc213.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F104154_d024b75529cbd1063709822da74dc213.png&h=4aab5f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地久天長搵極都搵唔到。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/104316_6a19990dc167e06f2ffbb523577aa07b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F104316_6a19990dc167e06f2ffbb523577aa07b.png&h=0082c777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為樓主一個post 揭開左一本十幾年無揭過既書"},{"pid":"ab6e347f6d7f2bfd209633fdf5abae71b10b44df","tid":758663,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b20279ceadb92636a0322e6b2d3fd8d19c753b2","tid":758663,"uid":30272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/104154_d024b75529cbd1063709822da74dc213.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F104154_d024b75529cbd1063709822da74dc213.png&h=4aab5f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地久天長搵極都搵唔到。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/104316_6a19990dc167e06f2ffbb523577aa07b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F104316_6a19990dc167e06f2ffbb523577aa07b.png&h=0082c777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為樓主一個post 揭開左一本十幾年無揭過既書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"依本書果陣睇好深刻，睇到喊"},{"pid":"2f9bddcbbdcfcca0220c97ee027fdaafd21b55ec","tid":758663,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:58:13.000Z","msg":"地久天長我有隻dvd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a312600d65409b75a8fa75176a79e7ac988402","tid":758663,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f9bddcbbdcfcca0220c97ee027fdaafd21b55ec","tid":758663,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:58:13.000Z","msg":"地久天長我有隻dvd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"張艾嘉"},{"pid":"14179f7877bdf336447c9601809709e8cd6134ae","tid":758663,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:18:58.000Z","msg":"中學睇過，會睇到好心酸"},{"pid":"86abc815b64aae9c35458459089f7d6c84a4fa24","tid":758663,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16a312600d65409b75a8fa75176a79e7ac988402","tid":758663,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f9bddcbbdcfcca0220c97ee027fdaafd21b55ec","tid":758663,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:58:13.000Z","msg":"地久天長我有隻dvd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"張艾嘉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"我有VCD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個男主角拍完收左皮"},{"pid":"9266dfb9fb05561f408db640fa9db2164f7b2cc8","tid":758663,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86abc815b64aae9c35458459089f7d6c84a4fa24","tid":758663,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16a312600d65409b75a8fa75176a79e7ac988402","tid":758663,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f9bddcbbdcfcca0220c97ee027fdaafd21b55ec","tid":758663,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:58:13.000Z","msg":"地久天長我有隻dvd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"張艾嘉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"我有VCD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個男主角拍完收左皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:08:11.000Z","msg":"邊個做男主"},{"pid":"e68206eda449db550d3fe16ca966a16326a77fb3","tid":758663,"uid":79353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:09:45.000Z","msg":"你喺度講呢啲陳年舊事，00後點會識應你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa